romo.DJ website, you consent to the data practices described in this statement.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; \"><b>Collection of your Personal Information </b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; \">Elite Promo.DJ collects personally identifiable information, such as your e-mail address, name, home or work address or telephone number. Elite Promo.DJ also collects anonymous demographic information, which is not unique to you, such as your postcode, age, gender, preferences, interests and favourites.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; \">There is also information about your computer hardware and software that is automatically collected by Elite Promo.DJ. This information can include: your IP address, browser type, domain names, access times and referring Web site addresses. This information is used by Elite Promo.DJ for the operation of the service, to maintain quality of the service, and to provide general statistics regarding use of the Elite Promo.DJ Web site.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; \">Please keep in mind that if you directly disclose personally identifiable information or personally sensitive data through Elite Promo.DJ public message boards, this information may be collected and used by others. Note: Elite Promo.DJ does not read any of your private online communications.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; \">Elite Promo.DJ encourages you to review the privacy statements of Web sites you choose to link to from Elite Promo.DJ ltd so that you can understand how those Web sites collect, use and share your information. Elite Promo.DJ is not responsible for the privacy statements or other content on Web sites outside of the Elite Promo.DJ and Elite Promo.DJ family of Web sites.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; \"><b>Use of your Personal Information</b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; \">Elite Promo.DJ collects and uses your personal information to operate the Elite Promo.DJ Web site and deliver the services you have requested. Elite Promo.DJ also uses your personally identifiable information to inform you of other products or services available from Elite Promo.DJ and its affiliates. Elite Promo.DJ may also contact you via surveys to conduct research about your opinion of current services or of potential new services that may be offered.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; \">Elite Promo.DJ does not sell, rent or lease its customer lists to third parties. Elite Promo.DJ may, from time to time, contact you on behalf of external business partners about a particular offering that may be of interest to you. In those cases, your unique personally identifiable information (e-mail, name, address, telephone number) is not transferred to the third party. In addition, Elite Promo.DJ may share data with trusted partners to help us perform statistical analysis, send you email or postal mail, provide customer support, or arrange for deliveries. All such third parties are prohibited from using your personal information except to provide these services to Elite Promo.DJ, and they are required to maintain the confidentiality of your information.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; \">Elite Promo.DJ does not use or disclose sensitive personal information, such as race, religion, or political affiliations, without your explicit consent.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; \">Elite Promo.DJ keeps track of the Web sites and pages our customers visit within Elite Promo.DJ, in order to determine what services are the most popular. This data is used to deliver customized content and advertising within Elite Promo.DJ to customers whose behaviour indicates that they are interested in a particular subject area. Elite Promo.DJ Web sites will disclose your personal information, without notice, only if required to do so by 